menu.name: Cheese Burger
menu.description: Juicy aged beef patty on a butter-toasted brioche bun. Melty American-style cheese and pickles for added flavor. Perfect for burger lovers!

menu.name: Margarita
menu.description: The Margarita pizza is a classic Italian dish made with a crispy crust, topped with tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, and fresh basil. This simple yet delicious pizza is perfect for those looking for a taste of Italy in every bite. Enjoy this classic pizza on its own or customize it with your choice of toppings.

menu.name: Vegetarian Pizza
menu.description: A delicious and healthy option for vegetarians, this pizza is made with a gluten-free crust and topped with a variety of fresh vegetables. Perfect for those looking for a tasty and nutritious meal.

menu.description: The Pepperoni Inferno pizza is not for the faint of heart! This spicy pie is loaded with spicy pepperoni, jalapeno peppers, and a spicy tomato sauce. The pizza is finished with a generous helping of melted mozzarella cheese and a sprinkle of red pepper flakes for an extra kick.

menu.name: Meat Lovers
menu.description: The Meat Lovers pizza is a carnivore's dream, with a generous helping of pepperoni, sausage, ham, and bacon. This pizza is sure to satisfy even the heartiest of appetites and is finished with a layer of melted mozzarella cheese.

menu.name: Eggplant Parmesan
